Breaking bad is one of it's kind. Perfect story ,perfect way to show the story. Perfect acting ,perfect directing. Great ending. I can watch this series again and again and it will stay the best. I recommend people to stop wasting their time and watch the most perfect series of all time in my opinion. Thanks Vince for this amazing show and i hope every creator to learn from breaking bad. Also, Bryan was absolutely stunning and he was perfect for the role ,Anna gunn deserved the Emmy And all the casting crew was great.Also,the choosing of characters is brilliant. PEOPLE !!! Don't miss this show, it's the best. It's 10/10 perfection.